fy-between gap-4 px-4 py-3 sm:px-6 lg:px-8"><a class="flex items-center gap-3" href="/Troptions-full-pack/"><img alt="TROPTIONS" width="40" height="40" decoding="async" data-nimg="1" class="rounded-full" style="color:transparent" src="/Troptions-full-pack/logo.png"/><span class="text-sm font-semibold tracking-wide text-white sm:text-base">TROPTIONS</span></a><nav class="hidden items-center gap-6 text-sm text-[var(--color-muted)] md:flex"><a href="#story" class="transition hover:text-[var(--color-gold-light)]">Story</a><a href="#pillars" class="transition hover:text-[var(--color-gold-light)]">Ecosystem</a><a href="#engineering" class="transition hover:text-[var(--color-gold-light)]">Engineering</a><a href="#truth" class="transition hover:text-[var(--color-gold-light)]">Truth labels</a><a href="#anthem" class="transition hover:text-[var(--color-gold-light)]">Anthem</a><a href="#contact" class="transition hover:text-[var(--color-gold-light)]">Contact</a><a class="transition hover:text-[var(--color-gold-light)]" href="/Troptions-full-pack/anthem/">Lyrics</a></nav></div></header><main><section class="relative overflow-hidden pb-20 pt-16 md:pb-28 md:pt-24"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 bg-[radial-gradient(ellipse_at_top,_rgba(184,134,11,0.12)_0%,_transparent_55%)]"></div><div class="relative mx-auto max-w-6xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8"><div class="flex flex-col gap-10 md:flex-row md:items-center md:gap-14"><div class="flex-1"><p class="text-sm font-medium uppercase tracking-widest text-[var(--color-gold)]">Investor showcase</p><h1 class="mt-4 text-3xl font-bold leading-tight text-white sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl">TROPTIONS – 22 Years. 9.0/10 Maturity. Sovereign by Default.</h1><p class="mt-6 max-w-2xl text-lg text-[var(--color-muted)]">Operating company plus open monorepo: Rust L1, DAO, Academy, TTN, Exchange OS, and multi-chain contracts — with honest labels for what is live, pipeline, or gated.</p><div class="mt-10 flex flex-wrap gap-4"><a href="https://fthtrading.github.io/Troptions-full-pack/technical/proof" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-[var(--color-gold)] px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-black transition hover:bg-[var(--color-gold-light)]" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">View Proof</a><a href="https://github.com/FTHTrading/Troptions-full-pack" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-lg border border-[var(--color-border)] bg-[var(--color-surface-elevated)] px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white transition hover:border-[var(--color-gold)]" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Clone Repo</a></div></div><div class="flex shrink-0 justify-center md:justify-end"><img alt="TROPTIONS logo" width="200" height="200" decoding="async" data-nimg="1" class="rounded-2xl shadow-2xl ring-1 ring-[var(--color-border)]" style="color:transparent" src="/Troptions-full-pack/logo.png"/></div></div></div></section><section id="story" class="scroll-mt-20 border-t border-[var(--color-border)] py-16 md:py-24 "><div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8"><header class="mb-10 md:mb-14"><h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-white md:text-3xl">Story</h2><p class="mt-3 max-w-3xl text-base text-[var(--color-muted)] md:text-lg">Macon 2003 → SEC chapter → sovereign stack today. Narrative for diligence; not legal advice.</p></header><ol class="relative border-l border-[var(--color-border)] pl-8"><li class="pb-10"><span class="absolute -left-[9px] mt-1.5 h-4 w-4 rounded-full border-2 border-[var(--color-gold)] bg-[var(--color-surface)]"></span><p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-[var(--color-gold)]">2003</p><h3 class="mt-1 text-lg font-semibold text-white">Macon origins</h3><p class="mt-2 max-w-3xl text-[var(--color-muted)]">Trade-credit and community-commerce concept in Macon, Georgia — alternative settlement before crypto was mainstream.</p></li><li class="pb-10"><span class="absolute -left-[9px] mt-1.5 h-4 w-4 rounded-full border-2 border-[var(--color-gold)] bg-[var(--color-surface)]"></span><p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-[var(--color-gold)]">2004+</p><h3 class="mt-1 text-lg font-semibold text-white">Washington &amp; SEC chapter</h3><p class="mt-2 max-w-3xl text-[var(--color-muted)]">Regulatory attention and structured response. Materials in-repo document compliance posture; counsel review required for external legal characterization.</p></li><li class="pb-10"><span class="absolute -left-[9px] mt-1.5 h-4 w-4 rounded-full border-2 border-[var(--color-gold)] bg-[var(--color-surface)]"></span><p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-[var(--color-gold)]">Legal</p><h3 class="mt-1 text-lg font-semibold text-white">Books clean, brand endures</h3><p class="mt-2 max-w-3xl text-[var(--color-muted)]">Operator narrative: every dime accounted for, no charges dropped — TROPTIONS continued building through headlines and doubt.</p></li><li class=""><span class="absolute -left-[9px] mt-1.5 h-4 w-4 rounded-full border-2 border-[var(--color-gold)] bg-[var(--color-surface)]"></span><p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-[var(--color-gold)]">Today</p><h3 class="mt-1 text-lg font-semibold text-white">Operating company + sovereign stack</h3><p class="mt-2 max-w-3xl text-[var(--color-muted)]">Academy, TTN, Exchange OS, launcher, and Troptions-full-pack L1/DAO — live on unykorn.org; troptions.org subdomains when DNS enables.</p></li></ol></div></section><section id="stack" class="scroll-mt-20 border-t border-[var(--color-border)] py-16 md:py-24 "><div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8"><header class="mb-10 md:mb-14"><h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-white md:text-3xl">Operating company · Sovereign stack · Proof</h2><p class="mt-3 max-w-3xl text-base text-[var(--color-muted)] md:text-lg">Three lenses for the same diligence conversation.</p></header><div class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-3"><article class="rounded-xl border border-[var(--color-border)] bg-[var(--color-surface-elevated)] p-6"><h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-[var(--color-gold-light)]">Operating Company</h3><ul class="mt-4 space-y-3 text-sm text-[var(--color-muted)]"><li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-[var(--color-gold)]">▸</span><span>FTH Trading brand: education, broadcast, exchange surfaces, token launch</span></li><li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-[var(--color-gold)]">▸</span><span>22-year continuity — Macon to sovereign infrastructure</span></li><li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-[var(--color-gold)]">▸</span><span>Live revenue: Academy tiers, launcher fees, sponsorship pipeline</span></li><li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-[var(--color-gold)]">▸</span><span>Eight Genesis brand domains in registry</span></li></ul></article><article class="rounded-xl border border-[var(--color-border)] bg-[var(--color-surface-elevated)] p-6"><h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-[var(--color-gold-light)]">Sovereign Stack</h3><ul class="mt-4 space-y-3 text-sm text-[var(--color-muted)]"><li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-[var(--color-gold)]">▸</span><span>Rust L1: RocksDB, treasury multisig, soulbound, settlement</span></li><li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-[var(--color-gold)]">▸</span><span>Sovereign Namespace Protocol (SNP) — 955 roots, Dilithium5, stateless verification</span></li><li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-[var(--color-gold)]">▸</span><span>DAO layer with governance API and dashboard</span></li><li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-[var(--color-gold)]">▸</span><span>Python/AI backends: Academy, DONK, TTN, DAO service</span></li><li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-[var(--color-gold)]">▸</span><span>Multi-chain: Polygon KENNY, XRPL gateway, Solana launcher</span></li></ul></article><article class="rounded-xl border border-[var(--color-border)] bg-[var(--color-surface-elevated)] p-6"><h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-[var(--color-gold-light)]">Proof &amp; Trust</h3><ul class="mt-4 space-y-3 text-sm text-[var(--color-muted)]"><li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-[var(--color-gold)]">▸</span><span>Truth labels: CONFIRMED vs PENDING with proof paths</span></li><li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-[var(--color-gold)]">▸</span><span>Domain truth table: LIVE vs Future DNS vs local dev</span></li><li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-[var(--color-gold)]">▸</span><span>On-chain refs: KENNY Polygon, XRPL gateway in docs</span></li><li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-[var(--color-gold)]">▸</span><span>No kill_switch in repo — honesty over hype</span></li></ul></article></div></div></section><section id="pillars" class="scroll-mt-20 border-t border-[var(--color-border)] py-16 md:py-24 "><div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8"><header class="mb-10 md:mb-14"><h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-white md:text-3xl">Revenue &amp; ecosystem</h2><p class="mt-3 max-w-3xl text-base text-[var(--color-muted)] md:text-lg">Honest map: live surfaces, namespace trust (SNP), pipeline sponsorship, and gated or attestation-only claims.</p></header><div class="grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2"><article class="flex flex-col rounded-xl border border-[var(--color-border)] bg-[var(--color-surface-elevated)] p-5"><div class="flex flex-wrap items-start justify-between gap-2"><h3 class="font-semibold text-white">FTH Academy</h3><span class="inline-flex shrink-0 items-center rounded-full px-2.5 py-0.5 text-xs font-medium uppercase tracking-wide ring-1 ring-inset bg-emerald-500/15 text-emerald-300 ring-emerald-500/30">Live</span></div><p class="mt-3 flex-1 text-sm text-[var(--color-muted)]">$19 / $49 / $149 subscription tiers</p><a href="https://fthedu.unykorn.org" class="mt-4 text-sm text-[var(--color-gold-light)] hover:underline" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Open surface →</a></article><article class="flex flex-col rounded-xl border border-[var(--color-border)] bg-[var(--color-surface-elevated)] p-5"><div class="f