over:underline" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Open surface →</a></article><article class="flex flex-col rounded-xl border border-[var(--color-border)] bg-[var(--color-surface-elevated)] p-5"><div class="flex flex-wrap items-start justify-between gap-2"><h3 class="font-semibold text-white">Polygon community (KENNY / EVL)</h3><span class="inline-flex shrink-0 items-center rounded-full px-2.5 py-0.5 text-xs font-medium uppercase tracking-wide ring-1 ring-inset bg-emerald-500/15 text-emerald-300 ring-emerald-500/30">Live</span></div><p class="mt-3 flex-1 text-sm text-[var(--color-muted)]">Mainnet addresses in proof docs</p></article><article class="flex flex-col rounded-xl border border-[var(--color-border)] bg-[var(--color-surface-elevated)] p-5"><div class="flex flex-wrap items-start justify-between gap-2"><h3 class="font-semibold text-white">T-Lev-8 RWA deal room</h3><span class="inline-flex shrink-0 items-center rounded-full px-2.5 py-0.5 text-xs font-medium uppercase tracking-wide ring-1 ring-inset bg-emerald-500/15 text-emerald-300 ring-emerald-500/30">Live</span></div><p class="mt-3 flex-1 text-sm text-[var(--color-muted)]">Partner licensing surface</p><a href="https://fthtrading.github.io/T-Lev-8-/" class="mt-4 text-sm text-[var(--color-gold-light)] hover:underline" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Open surface →</a></article><article class="flex flex-col rounded-xl border border-[var(--color-border)] bg-[var(--color-surface-elevated)] p-5"><div class="flex flex-wrap items-start justify-between gap-2"><h3 class="font-semibold text-white">x402 facilitator (main branch)</h3><span class="inline-flex shrink-0 items-center rounded-full px-2.5 py-0.5 text-xs font-medium uppercase tracking-wide ring-1 ring-inset bg-sky-500/15 text-sky-200 ring-sky-500/30">Gated</span></div><p class="mt-3 flex-1 text-sm text-[var(--color-muted)]">Code on main; production LOCAL_ONLY. Public health on UnyKorn AWS</p><a href="https://x402.unykorn.org/health" class="mt-4 text-sm text-[var(--color-gold-light)] hover:underline" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Open surface →</a></article><article class="flex flex-col rounded-xl border border-[var(--color-border)] bg-[var(--color-surface-elevated)] p-5"><div class="flex flex-wrap items-start justify-between gap-2"><h3 class="font-semibold text-white">Sovereign Namespace Protocol (SNP)</h3><span class="inline-flex shrink-0 items-center rounded-full px-2.5 py-0.5 text-xs font-medium uppercase tracking-wide ring-1 ring-inset bg-emerald-500/15 text-emerald-300 ring-emerald-500/30">Live</span></div><p class="mt-3 flex-1 text-sm text-[var(--color-muted)]">Constitutional namespace layer — 955 roots, Dilithium5, stateless verification. Root trust primitive of the FTH/UnyKorn stack.</p><a href="https://github.com/FTHTrading/sovereign-namespace-protocol" class="mt-4 text-sm text-[var(--color-gold-light)] hover:underline" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Open surface →</a></article></div></div></section><section id="engineering" class="scroll-mt-20 border-t border-[var(--color-border)] py-16 md:py-24 "><div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8"><header class="mb-10 md:mb-14"><h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-white md:text-3xl">Engineering maturity</h2><p class="mt-3 max-w-3xl text-base text-[var(--color-muted)] md:text-lg">Production hardening on main — with explicit gaps, not hidden debt.</p></header><div class="mb-10 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-4"><div class="flex h-24 w-24 flex-col items-center justify-center rounded-2xl border-2 border-[var(--color-gold)] bg-[var(--color-gold)]/10"><span class="text-3xl font-bold text-[var(--color-gold-light)]">9.0</span><span class="text-xs text-[var(--color-muted)]">/ 10</span></div><p class="max-w-xl text-sm text-[var(--color-muted)]">TLS templates, API-key writes, DAO reads L1 directly, signed governance RPC. Sovereign Sequencer — single-node today; BFT planned.</p></div><div class="grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-2"><div><h3 class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-emerald-400">Built &amp; confirmed</h3><ul class="mt-4 space-y-2 text-sm text-[var(--color-muted)]"><li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-emerald-500">✓</span>11 Rust L1 crates + integration tests (~28 cargo tests)</li><li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-emerald-500">✓</span>13 pytest (backend + DAO)</li><li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-emerald-500">✓</span>RocksDB persistence, treasury multisig, signed submit tests</li><li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-emerald-500">✓</span>TLS nginx templates, API-key auth, DAO↔L1 reads</li><li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-emerald-500">✓</span>Live unykorn.org surfaces (hub, sports, launcher, academy)</li><li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-emerald-500">✓</span>KENNY Polygon mainnet + XRPL gateway documented</li></ul></div><div><h3 class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-amber-400">Gaps &amp; pending</h3><ul class="mt-4 space-y-2 text-sm text-[var(--color-muted)]"><li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-amber-500">○</span>Public TLS on troptions.org hostnames (DNS + certbot pending)</li><li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-amber-500">○</span>Fraud proofs — design only (Q4 2026 target)</li><li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-amber-500">○</span>ai.troptions.org / ttn / dao troptions DNS — Future DNS</li><li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-amber-500">○</span>x402 on main: LOCAL_ONLY; Apostle AWS on feature branch</li><li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-amber-500">○</span>Single-node Sovereign Sequencer (not BFT multi-validator)</li><li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-amber-500">○</span>Exchange desk $175M — attestation only, not verified fact</li></ul></div></div></div></section><section id="truth" class="scroll-mt-20 border-t border-[var(--color-border)] py-16 md:py-24 "><div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8"><header class="mb-10 md:mb-14"><h2 class="text-2xl font-semibo